# Quality Gates

No task is complete until verification is run for touched scope.

Required behavior:

- Run focused checks first, then broaden only if needed.
- Report what was run, what passed, and any remaining risk.
- If checks fail, fix failures before expanding scope.

Default commands (by change scope):

| Scope | Command |
| --- | --- |
| Harness / docs | `./scripts/check-canonical-drift.sh` |
| Milestone close | See `.cursor/skills/milestone-gate/SKILL.md` |
| `.ngb` tools (M2+) | `./scripts/check-ngb-roundtrip.sh` when present |
| Probe (M3+) | `./scripts/check-probe-audit-log.sh` when present |
| C tools | `make -C tools test` or project README when added |

If no automated harness exists for the milestone yet, state manual verification and add the script in the same milestone when possible.
